message.text:
KANJI Quiz!
Do you know the meaning of the Kanji "祭"？ Choose the answer!
「祭」の意味はどれ？
1. forget 2. name 3. festival

NO Festival, NO Summer!!! Japan is full of various festivals especially in summer, from traditional ones with huge fireworks to small community ones with delicious local foods, literally everywhere in Japan!

"Hanabi（花火）", fireworks, "Yukata（浴衣）", a casual summer kimono, "Yatai（屋台)", a mobile food stall,  "Taiko（太鼓）", Japanese percussion instruments etc... What does a "festival" remind you?
http://www.anime-manga.jp/KanjiGame/School/　　

日本の夏は「お祭り」なしでは語れません！おいしい食べ物、踊り、歌、花火・・・あなたは「お祭り」と聞いて、何を思い浮かべますか？

message.text:
"Evangelion and Japanese Swords" Madrid Exhibition has opened!
On the opening day, July 4th, many people visited and enjoyed the exhibition.
At the exhibition, you can learn how to enjoy the highlight of Japanese swords, which makes the exhibition more interesting!
From Jul. 5 to Sep. 28 ：Museo ABC (Madrid, Spain)

ヱヴァンゲリヲンと日本刀展・マドリード展、オープンしました！7/4の内覧会は満員御礼。会場では、日本刀鑑賞のポイントも学べますよ♪鑑賞が何倍も面白くなること間違いなし！
９月２８日まで、ABCミュージアム（スペイン・マドリード市）にて。
http://www.jpf.go.jp/e/culture/new/1401/01-01.html
http://museo.abc.es/es/exposicion/312

See more details in the article here.
http://ramenparados.blogspot.com.es/2014/07/exposicion-evangelion-y-las-katanas_9.html

message.text:
Australia: Aug 27 Takarazuka Revue- The Allure of Gender-Bending Musical Theatre
Discover the world of a unique musical theatre company known for lavishly-costumed performances by all-female casts who play both male and female roles, which is celebrating the 100th anniversary of its founding this year!
http://www.jpf.org.au/jpfevents/14-noh-to-now/5.html
オーストラリア：8/27 宝塚 レクチャー・シリーズ 宝塚歌劇団
今年で100周年を迎える、華麗できらびやかな宝塚歌劇の世界をオーストラリア人研究者が解説！
Photo: Takarazuka Revue
